WEBVTT

00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:08.189
Early in the morning on September 20, 2016, armed law enforcement officers in masks forced

00:00:08.189 --> 00:00:12.710
their way into religious building of Jehovah's Witnesses in the village of Nizloubnaya,

00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:13.710
Stavra Polterritory.

00:00:13.710 --> 00:00:20.550
I was keeping watch in the building when I saw on the monitor that several vehicles

00:00:20.550 --> 00:00:25.789
had driven up and people in black masks got out.

00:00:25.789 --> 00:00:29.070
They jumped over the fence and broke the lock on the gate.

00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:33.509
They drove their vehicle into our property and began using a circular saw to cut the

00:00:33.509 --> 00:00:35.869
entry door.

00:00:35.869 --> 00:00:38.750
They cut the hinges and entered the building.

00:00:38.750 --> 00:00:44.070
When they saw me, they said, hands out of your pockets and go outside.

00:00:44.070 --> 00:00:49.429
The security camera footage shows the officers spreading out in the building.

00:00:49.429 --> 00:00:53.789
Several officers entered the hall on the first floor, and two of them, in the presence

00:00:53.789 --> 00:00:58.189
of their colleagues, pulled band literature out from under their clothing and placed it

00:00:58.189 --> 00:01:02.030
in a cabinet nearby.

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:06.189
We regularly inspect our religious building to make sure there are no strange items or

00:01:06.189 --> 00:01:08.189
band literature.

00:01:08.189 --> 00:01:13.269
As usual, an inspection had been made the night before, and there was nothing in this cabinet.

00:01:13.269 --> 00:01:16.069
It was empty.

00:01:16.069 --> 00:01:20.829
But the security camera footage clearly shows officers supposedly seizing literature

00:01:20.829 --> 00:01:27.030
from this part of the cabinet, while the other shelves were still empty.

00:01:27.030 --> 00:01:32.150
The law enforcement officers also seized audio and video equipment.

00:01:32.150 --> 00:01:36.469
When the representative of the building's owner arrived, the officers did not permit him

00:01:36.469 --> 00:01:41.069
to participate in the search.

00:01:41.069 --> 00:01:46.629
The officer who was in charge of the search did not identify himself and did not let me

00:01:46.629 --> 00:01:48.750
see the search order.

00:01:48.750 --> 00:01:56.030
When I asked him to give me a copy of the order, he rudely demanded that I leave the building,

00:01:56.030 --> 00:02:00.870
so I had no choice but to comply and leave the building.

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:03.909
These actions included multiple violations of the law.

00:02:03.909 --> 00:02:08.069
For example, the search order was not shown to anyone, even though there were people in

00:02:08.069 --> 00:02:09.069
the building.

00:02:09.069 --> 00:02:12.629
But that matter, the forced entry was unlawful from the start.

00:02:12.629 --> 00:02:17.389
They did not even give the people inside the building the option to open the door voluntarily.

00:02:17.389 --> 00:02:20.069
They immediately used special equipment.

00:02:20.069 --> 00:02:24.509
Also the law enforcement officers exceeded their authority by ordering the building owner's

00:02:24.509 --> 00:02:27.949
representative to leave the place being searched.

00:02:27.949 --> 00:02:32.310
Another search was being made at the same time in the home of Pavel Puzaryov, the chairman

00:02:32.310 --> 00:02:38.349
of the Committee of the Local Religious Organization of Jehovah's Witnesses, village of Nizlodna.

00:02:38.349 --> 00:02:40.669
Some of the officers jumped over the fence.

00:02:40.669 --> 00:02:43.310
When they entered our home, there were about ten of them.

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:47.669
They immediately spread out into different rooms, so we were not able to observe everything

00:02:47.669 --> 00:02:49.310
going on during the search.

00:02:49.310 --> 00:02:53.629
For example, the first items were planted here in the kitchen.

00:02:53.629 --> 00:02:58.229
As a result of these searches, protocols of administrative violations against the witnesses

00:02:58.229 --> 00:02:59.750
were filled out.

00:02:59.750 --> 00:03:04.509
Interestingly, just one week before these events, Pavel Puzaryov had been the victim of another

00:03:04.509 --> 00:03:06.030
tactic.

00:03:06.030 --> 00:03:10.310
Someone had posted flyers, supposedly from him, in college buildings.

00:03:10.310 --> 00:03:14.710
The director of a college called me and said that some flyers had been posted in her

00:03:14.710 --> 00:03:21.150
college with a message along the lines of, get on the path of truth, pray to Jehovah.

00:03:21.150 --> 00:03:25.430
Below, the flyer listed my phone number and the Kingdom Hall phone number.

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:29.810
Jehovah's Witnesses believe that this demonstrates the intent of the authorities to ban the

00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:34.550
local religious organization of Jehovah's Witnesses, which has operated legally in the village

00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:38.750
of Nizlodna for 17 years.

00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:44.830
The last time homes of Jehovah's Witnesses in Nizlodna were searched was in 1985.

00:03:44.830 --> 00:03:49.550
Back then, Jehovah's Witnesses knew that law enforcement officers could come at any time

00:03:49.550 --> 00:03:52.550
and seize their Bible or their Bible literature.

00:03:52.550 --> 00:03:59.349
History is repeating itself, but now, in 2016, even if you don't have anything banned,

00:03:59.349 --> 00:04:01.550
it can be planted in your possession.

00:04:01.550 --> 00:04:07.750
There have been no fewer than 60 incidents of planted and falsified evidence, and in

00:04:07.750 --> 00:04:11.789
most cases, the worshippers could only throw up their hands helplessly.

00:04:11.789 --> 00:04:16.589
However, when the planting of evidence is recorded on video, incidents such as this

00:04:16.589 --> 00:04:20.230
one in Nizlodna reveal the sad truth.

00:04:20.230 --> 00:04:24.550
The evidence is planted by the very ones who should uphold law and order.

00:04:24.550 --> 00:04:26.149
It is on their conscience.

00:04:26.149 --> 00:04:29.509
It is their responsibility before God and man.
